CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Crowd of women and men, including woman wearing light colored gown with sequined sash and man wearing diner jacket, smoking cigarette, gathered in interior with floral and leaf patterned carpeting for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc.
